snippet: The airplane, which was bound for Madrid, made an emergency landing after a passenger alerted an air marshal to an object that appeared out of the ordinary.
abstract: Delta Air Lines flight flight bound for Madrid, Spain, out of Kennedy Airport is forced to make an emergency landing after a passenger alerted an air marshal of a suspicious package in a bathroom on board.
lead_paragraph: The airplane, which was bound for Madrid, made an emergency landing after a passenger alerted an air marshal to an object that appeared out of the ordinary.

headline.seo: Plane Returns to Kennedy Airport After Suspicious Package Is Found
